FinClaw integration changes include:
- Bundling TradingAgents AStock as a FinClaw capability under capabilities/
- Routing A-share data through FinClaw / FinDataHub by default
- Adding a self-contained HTML report renderer without BettaFish ReportEngine
- Removing direct BettaFish coupling from the capability integration path

See capabilities/tradingagents_astock/NOTICE and
capabilities/tradingagents_astock/CHANGES_FROM_UPSTREAM.md for upstream
attribution and detailed modifications.

